      "text": "As a farmer's son, Werner Schwarz grew up at the beginning of the 20th century, cultivated the fields of art until his death and still moves his fellow men to wonder today. The documentary film follows in the footsteps of the well-traveled, explorative artist and shows a life lived to the point of absolute devotion. A powerful portrait of an outsider who becomes a center of attraction."
